description: Spectacular waterfront one bedroom + den, 1.5 Bathroom at Pier 4!  This sun splashed home with unobstructed water views offers a lovely open concept floor-plan with private balcony and top of the line finishes. The unit features soaring ceilings, walnut flooring, and gourmet chefs kitchen boasting sleek cabinetry, waterfall marble island, and Gaggenau appliances.  The master suite overlooks the harbor and features a gorgeous marble bathroom with double vanity and walk-in shower. Additional den is perfect for home office, nursery, or out of town guests. Pier 4 is a boutique style building consisting of 106 homes, offering a suite of amenities including a state of the art gym, golf simulator, 24 hour concierge, doorman, resident lounge, fire pit, grill and common terrace overlooking the water. Includes one deeded parking space and additional storage..
